---
import MainGridLayout from '../layouts/MainGridLayout.astro'
const currentNode = import.meta.env.SITE_NODE_NAME || "未知节点"
---

<MainGridLayout title="节点列表" description="多线路节点导航">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">🌐 节点列表</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
      当前节点: <span class="font-semibold text-primary">{currentNode}</span>
    </p>

    <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        这里是博客的多线路节点汇总页。<br>
        为了方便访问，我搭建了一个独立的节点状态页面，你可以在那里查看所有节点的实时延迟和在线状态，并选择最快的线路访问。
      </p>
      
      <a 
        href="https://nodes.thelittlequtegdh.fun"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-gray-900 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-colors font-medium"
      >
        <span>前往节点状态页</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
      <p>如果当前节点访问缓慢或无法使用，建议前往节点状态页选择其他线路。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainGridLayout>
